    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo propagation confirms NIH prediction intervals are within acceptable bounds relative to the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
